Hack Nerd Font — the Hack typeface (© Source Foundry Authors, MIT) patched with
Nerd Fonts glyphs (ryanoasis/nerd-fonts, MIT). Bundled from Nerd Fonts v3.4.0.
Hack incorporates DejaVu (public domain) and Bitstream Vera (Bitstream Vera License,
reserved names "Bitstream"/"Vera"). Full license text ships in the font's own name
table and at github.com/source-foundry/Hack and github.com/ryanoasis/nerd-fonts.
